"><div class = \"text-block\">Axenic cultures protocol<\/div><div class = \"text-block\">Axenicity of cultures is obtained by multi-antibiotic treatment:  by adding antibiotics directly to the medium in which the strain will be inoculated. After a variable amount of days we refresh the coltures with new medium.<\/div><\/div>","changed_on":1590486692}